{"tid":2029101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［將軍澳街坊入］大家留意下「公屋居民關愛會」呢個組織","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:42:16.000Z","uid":263560,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb44f415eaf1aa0feed1a4a04d822dadb7f6fd64","tid":2029101,"uid":263560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n屋企人喺啲屋邨商場拎咗下面呢張「公屋居民關愛會」嘅入會表格返嚟<br />\n想我幫佢填 交咗表會送油送米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osH0XFi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosH0XFi.jpg&h=5e2312fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpBAMyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpBAMyE.jpg&h=4ab57bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再細心望一望份表格內容<br />\n呢個機構聲稱自己「不依附任何政治組織」<br />\n純服務基層市民、「共建和諧社會」<br />\n收集完個人資料之後<br />\n下面點解要問你是否選民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要問關於大灣區居住嘅問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後面嗰頁仲聲稱送一份10萬港元嘅意外保險<br />\n重點係下面你要填埋受益人/家人嘅個人資料<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網再search 呢個機構嘅名<br />\n搵到以下呢個facebook page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Local-Business/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B%E6%9C%83-238065893504318/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FLocal-Business%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%259C%2583-238065893504318%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSmyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b3eb0408\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Local-Business/%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B%E6%9C%83-238065893504318/</a><br />\n原來喺2018年開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李林昌</span></strong>已經喺馬鞍山落區<br />\n掛住呢個組織嘅牌頭參與沙田區區選<br />\n<br />\n大家再睇埋呢個人嘅背景：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZM5psn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZM5psn.png&h=a985e5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來又係愛国團體嘅分身之一<br />\n繼續行蛇齋餅糭路線之餘<br />\n今次仲玩收集選民資料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位巴打絲打麻煩留意下屋企人有冇拎咗呢份咁嘅表返嚟<br />\n有嘅千祈一定要掉咗佢唔好幫佢填<br />\n今次仲想借保險之名收集埋家人資料<br />\n千祈唔好比呢啲垃圾得逞啊</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立<br />\n唯一出路<br />\n各位星期日見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8f3bd82c57d2a03597b615837a465637433fea0d","tid":2029101,"uid":197873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"非街坊幫push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b25ca0a7c9849bb01c9fd3704050903f487f00","tid":2029101,"uid":263560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"大家除咗留意国安法之外<br />\n都要留意呢班垃圾人渣喺地區一路一路都做緊嘢"},{"pid":"debe4b6dfff6c7e7c51f208a190453422b3b18af","tid":2029101,"uid":28733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:48:08.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /